@startuml
title Auth Client Request Inference and Typing (Before)
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #000000
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas
skinparam defaultFontColor #000000
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam noteBorderColor #000000

actor "SDK Consumer" as Consumer #BBDEFB
component "auth.request(...)\nmethod inferred by body only" as RequestSurface #FFE082
component "Known endpoint families\n(session/account/etc.)" as EndpointFamilies #C5E1A5
component "Ad hoc inline response typing" as InlineTyping #FFCDD2

Consumer --> RequestSurface : request({ endpoint, body?, query? })
RequestSurface --> EndpointFamilies : GET when no body\nPOST when body exists
RequestSurface --> InlineTyping : some repeated inline types

note right of RequestSurface
No endpoint-aware default method inference.
POST endpoints without body can accidentally
default to GET unless caller sets method manually.
end note
@enduml
